properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Manasquan Inlet to Little Egg Inlet NJ out 20 nm; Coastal waters from Great Egg Inlet to Cape May NJ out 20 nm; Coastal waters from Little Egg Inlet to Great Egg Inlet NJ out 20 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 8 at 12:40AM EST until February 8 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 25 knots with gusts up to 30 knots and
seas 5 to 8 feet.

* WHERE...The coastal waters from Manasquan Inlet to Cape May,
New Jersey.

* WHEN...Until 1:00 PM this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating a small
vessel, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON... ...GALE WARNING IS CANCELLED
